text: Megan Schooling (born 1 May 1989) is a South African water polo player. She competed for the South Africa women's national water polo team in the 2013 World Aquatics Championships, 2015 World Aquatics Championships, and 2017 World Aquatics Championships. == References == ==Other websites == * Women's Water Polo Day Two - 14th FINA World Championships zimbio Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:South African water polo players
